anced by a combination of the grant funds from the Global Environment Facility (GEF) international waters focal area and from third parties through co-financing and parallel financing. The current direct co-financing stands at _2.0 million from The University of Queensland, however, parallel financing is also significant with _3.9 million in contributions from various research partners towards salary provisions, project management costs and other resources. An additional _21.9 million in parallel co-financing is contributed from World Bank projects directly linked to CCRES: a) Coral Reef Rehabilitation and Management Program-Coral Triangle Initiative (COREMAP-CTI), and b) Philippines rural development project, which are also part of the GEF IW scaling up partnership program.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Capturing Coral Reef Ecosystem Services (CCRES)',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Paper (PJPR),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PJPR',ENTITYID:'000356161_20130918145229',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000356161_20130918145229',DOCDATE:'04-SEP-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'090224b081e221fe_2_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081e221fe_2_0',DOCDATE:'21-AUG-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'000442464_20130826110229',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000442464_20130826110229',DOCDATE:'20-AUG-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'000333037_20130812105705',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000333037_20130812105705',DOCDATE:'25-JUL-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTY