opment objective (PDO) will be measured in terms of the following indicators: (a) direct project beneficiaries, percentage of whom are female; (b) people in urban areas provided with access to an improved water source under the project; and (c) increased capacity of the water system. The project is expected to directly benefit approximately 100,000 households in the Greater Maputo Area who will be directly connected to the formal water supply system in Greater Maputo and will be able to receive treated, piped water.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Greater Maputo Water Supply Expansion Project',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Appraisal Document (PAD),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PAD',ENTITYID:'000445729_20130710113721',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000445729_20130710113721',DOCDATE:'27-JUN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'090224b081c2d467_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081c2d467_1_0',DOCDATE:'05-JUN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'090224b081b8f182_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081b8f182_1_0',DOCDATE:'07-MAY-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Procurement Plan (PROP),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PROP',ENTITYID:'000333037_20130327122812',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000333037_20130327122812',DOCDATE:'26-MAR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Environmental Assessment (EA),  Vol.4 of 12',DOCTYPE:'EA',ENTITYID:'000356161_20130320153713',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000356161_20130320153713',DOCDATE:'01-MAR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_D