 (IADB), one of the co-financiers of the Project, in an effort to have the same monitoring and evaluation framework, facilitate supervision, and reduce the burden on the client. This PDO adequately reflects the objectives of the Project, is measurable and is, therefore, deemed appropriate.  The Project consists of the following five components: (i) construction of two metro stations of the Quito Metro Line One; (ii) infrastructure and equipment investment for the Quito Metro Line One; (iii) provision of train sets to operate in the Quito Metro Line One; (iv) Project Management; and (V) technical studies to support implementation.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Quito Metro Line One',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Board Summary (SU),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'SU',ENTITYID:'000445729_20130806123931',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000445729_20130806123931',DOCDATE:'25-JUL-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Appraisal Document (PAD),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PAD',ENTITYID:'000445729_20130709113927',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000445729_20130709113927',DOCDATE:'28-JUN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Appraisal Document (PAD),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PAD',ENTITYID:'000333037_20131009163948',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000333037_20131009163948',DOCDATE:'28-JUN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'090224b081c9e752_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081c9e752_1_0',DOCDATE:'23-JUN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'090224b081c757e9_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=d