 some recently emerged reform priorities. DPG V will support the reforms designed under the NDP in two broad areas: (a) strengthening the PA s fiscal position; and (b) laying the institutional foundations for improved governance and transparency in the public sector. The operation supports efforts seen as crucial by the PA to overcoming the urgent fiscal issues, reducing the PA s reliance on foreign assistance for recurrent expenditures while increasing the efficiency of government expenditure programs. In addition, the operation supports improving governance and transparency in the areas that are important for better management of public finances. DPG V, as envisaged in the 2012-2014 interim strategy note, remains a key instrument aimed at supporting the PA s strategic priorities, advancing the policy dialogue, and also providing essential financing for the PA s budget.'},PROJECT_NAME:'WBG - PRDP Support V',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Program Document (PGD),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PGD',ENTITYID:'000333037_20130507101304',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000333037_20130507101304',DOCDATE:'25-APR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'000356161_20130327115437',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000356161_20130327115437',DOCDATE:'26-MAR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.1',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'000001843_20130315092427',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000001843_20130315092427',DOCDATE:'13-MAR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'000104615_20121211170720',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000