 water users and improvements aggregated as the national level through allocation of water and rights. There are three components to the project; The first component is water resources management , the objective of this component is to enhance capacity at the national and regional level to address the challenges of water resources management in Zambia; The second component is water resources development , the objective of this component is to address the infrastructure deficit; and finally the third component is institutional support, the objective of this component is to strengthen the institutional capacity for water resources management and development.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Zambia Water Resources Development Project',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Appraisal Document (PAD),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PAD',ENTITYID:'000445729_20130410104810',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000445729_20130410104810',DOCDATE:'01-APR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'090224b0819febea_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b0819febea_1_0',DOCDATE:'19-FEB-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'090224b08194006f_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b08194006f_1_0',DOCDATE:'18-FEB-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Environmental Assessment (EA),  Vol.1 of 3',DOCTYPE:'EA',ENTITYID:'000442464_20130212111018',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000442464_20130212111018',DOCDATE:'01-FEB-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Resettlement Plan (RPL),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'RPL',ENTITYID:'000442464_20130212123456',DOCURL:'http://w