 electrification. It include three sub-components: (i) energy policy development; (ii) institutional and strategy development; and (iii) capacity building. The second component is technical assistance for preparation and planning for Port Moresby hydropower supply. It include two sub-components: (a) preparation of the Naoro Brown hydropower project for Port Moresby; and (b) improved planning related to hydropower supply for Port Moresby.'},PROJECT_NAME:'PNG Energy Sector Development Project',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Implementation Status and Results Report (ISRR),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISRR',ENTITYID:'090224b082056852_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b082056852_1_0',DOCDATE:'10-NOV-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'000350881_20130129081941',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000350881_20130129081941',DOCDATE:'25-JAN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Appraisal Document (PAD),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PAD',ENTITYID:'000442464_20130204131031',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000442464_20130204131031',DOCDATE:'22-JAN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'0000A8056_2011111718204002',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=0000A8056_2011111718204002',DOCDATE:'16-JAN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'0000A8056_2012080721513676',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=0000A8056_2012080721513676',DOCDATE:'07-AUG-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Environm