velopment objectives (PDO). All works contracts are awarded and are planned to be completed by September 30, 2015. The closing date for the original credit will be extended by two years from December 31, 2014 to December 31, 2016, to allow sufficient time to complete the works and to cover the first year of operation of the BRT system.'},PROJECT_NAME:'TANZANIA SECOND CENTRAL TRANSP CORRIDOR PROJECT - ADD L FINANC',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Summary of Discussion (Summary of Discussion),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'Summary of Discussion',ENTITYID:'000333037_20130128155606',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000333037_20130128155606',DOCDATE:'15-JAN-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Paper (PJPR),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PJPR',ENTITYID:'000333037_20121204001835',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000333037_20121204001835',DOCDATE:'27-NOV-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'000104615_20120815151948',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000104615_20120815151948',DOCDATE:'15-AUG-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'000104615_20120723121244',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000104615_20120723121244',DOCDATE:'23-JUL-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Resettlement Plan (RPL),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'RPL',ENTITYID:'000334955_20110125053441',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000334955_20110125053441',DOCDATE:'01-JAN-2011'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Environmental Assessment (EA),  Vol.1 of 2',DOCTYPE:'EA',ENTITYID:'000333037_20101130022