ildren by helping to bring about a system-wide transformation through pedagogical innovation. The GPE-VNEN project is a set of sequential activities that together constitute a comprehensive package of pedagogical and administrative reform. The project comprises four components: (1) Material development for pedagogical renovation, which includes the development of learning guides and other materials and capacity building for material development; (2) training and provision of materials; (3) school level support for VNEN implementation; and (4) project and knowledge management. '},PROJECT_NAME:'Vietnam:  Global Partnership for Education - Vietnam Escuela Nueva Project',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Implementation Status and Results Report (ISRR),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISRR',ENTITYID:'090224b081fe6601_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081fe6601_1_0',DOCDATE:'26-OCT-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Procurement Plan (PROP),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PROP',ENTITYID:'000442464_20130912110756',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000442464_20130912110756',DOCDATE:'30-AUG-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Disbursement Letter (Disbursement Letter),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'Disbursement Letter',ENTITYID:'090224b081c585d5_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081c585d5_1_0',DOCDATE:'15-MAY-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Implementation Status and Results Report (ISRR),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISRR',ENTITYID:'090224b081abdeb6_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081abdeb6_1_0',DOCDATE:'14-APR-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Procurement Plan (PROP),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PROP',ENTITYID:'000333037_20130412110936',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.or