in reasons for reduced financing were that the project was introducing new concepts and reengaging financially in the agriculture sector and it was felt that a smaller initial investment would be more prudent. The changes to the project are: a) extension of the closing date of the original project; b) revised project development objective to remove the restriction on project districts and scale up the scope of the project; and c) revised targets of outcome indicators to reflect scaling up of investments. This will require an amendment to the financing agreement for the current project. Extension of the closing date is being sought to ensure enough time for the scaled up programs to be completed and results to be documented.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Additional Financing for the Project for Agriculture Commercialization and Trade',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Paper (PJPR),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PJPR',ENTITYID:'000356161_20121101010534',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000356161_20121101010534',DOCDATE:'16-OCT-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'0000A8056_2012081418011912',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=0000A8056_2012081418011912',DOCDATE:'14-AUG-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (ISDS),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISDS',ENTITYID:'0000A8056_2012091319253041',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=0000A8056_2012091319253041',DOCDATE:'05-AUG-2012'}},PROJECTFINANCIALTYPE:'IDA',PROJECTSTATUSDISPLAY:'Active',REGIONNAME:'South Asia',SECTOR:{__NAME:{NAME:'Crops'},__NAME:{NAME:'Agro-industry, marketing, and trade'},__NAME:{NAME:'Public administration- Agriculture, fishing and forestry'},__NAME:{NAME:'Animal production'}},SECTOR1:{NAME:'Crops',PERCENT:39},SECTOR2:{NAME: