esearch; (ii) to increase the quality of higher education by, among others, upgrading faculty qualifications and fostering evaluation and accreditation; (iii) to increase relevance in higher education by focusing resources on priority subjects that are key to the country s development; and (iv) to strengthen public universities  management capacity and accountability. Finally, the second component is strengthening institutional capacity for quality enhancement. This component includes three sub-components: (a) strengthening the national system for the accreditation of higher education; (b) developing the labor market observatory and the public higher education information system; and (c) supporting the project s coordination, supervision, and evaluation.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Costa Rica Higher Education',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Implementation Status and Results Report (ISRR),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISRR',ENTITYID:'090224b081e828fe_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081e828fe_1_0',DOCDATE:'04-SEP-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Implementation Status and Results Report (ISRR),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'ISRR',ENTITYID:'090224b0818ec525_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b0818ec525_1_0',DOCDATE:'03-FEB-2013'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Disbursement Letter (Disbursement Letter),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'Disbursement Letter',ENTITYID:'090224b081778688_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081778688_1_0',DOCDATE:'06-NOV-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Loan Agreement (LA),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'LA',ENTITYID:'090224b081778650_1_0',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=090224b081778650_1_0',DOCDATE:'06-NOV-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Ap