estructured to reflect changes that include: (a) extension of the date for the hiring of an external auditor to November 30, 2012; (b) deletion of a redundant reference to an implementation manual; and (c) application of the new procurement guidelines (January 2011) upon effectiveness of the additional financing credit.'},PROJECT_NAME:'Road Asset Management Project - Additional Financing',PROJECTDOCS:{__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Paper (PJPR),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'PJPR',ENTITYID:'000406484_20120831111312',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000406484_20120831111312',DOCDATE:'23-AUG-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Project Information Document (PID),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'PID',ENTITYID:'0000A8056_2012061112053538',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=0000A8056_2012061112053538',DOCDATE:'11-JUN-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Integrated Safeguards Data Sheet (INTEGRATED SAFEGUARDS DATA SHEET),  Vol.',DOCTYPE:'INTEGRATED SAFEGUARDS DATA SHEET',ENTITYID:'0000A8056_2012060811413593',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=0000A8056_2012060811413593',DOCDATE:'08-JUN-2012'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Resettlement Plan (RPL),  Vol.1 of 1',DOCTYPE:'RPL',ENTITYID:'000386194_20120412004128',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000386194_20120412004128',DOCDATE:'01-OCT-2009'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Environmental Assessment (EA),  Vol.1 of 2',DOCTYPE:'EA',ENTITYID:'000356161_20120412005605',DOCURL:'http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSServlet?pcont=details&eid=000356161_20120412005605',DOCDATE:'01-JUN-2009'},__DOCDATE_DOCTYPE_DOCTYPEDESC_DOCURL_ENTITYID:{DOCTYPEDESC:'Environmental Assessment (EA),  Vol.2 of 2',DOCTYPE:'EA',ENTITYID:'000356161_20120412005822',DOCU